text: Kathy is the sales person I trust most when shopping at Fila. She is always enthusiastic, professional, and patiently answers my questions, making every shopping experience very satisfying. I learned that she is now at the Plaza Singapura branch, and I will definitely continue to support her!
Lovely service from Lucas Mak.  Went extra mile to fetch merchandise from another outlet without first asking for payment.  Thumbs up!
Proactive staffs who are welcoming and always ready to help :)
